           LIBS/explode.library
           LIBS/reqtools.library
           LIBS/xfdmaster.library
           LIBS/fileID.library
           DOCUMENTS/Virusworkshop.Guide
           DOCUMENTS/Virusworkshop.Guide.INFO
           DOCUMENTS/VWMemmon.Guide
