@node "excre" "excre"




        Excreminator Virus 1:
        ---------------------
        
        Filelength: 2392

        This is a very lame trojan horse. It changes NO vectors
        in memory. It simply loads at each call the file 
        "df0:libs/exec.library" and works with this 4 byte long
        file. The counter will be set to 5. If the value reaches
        0 (by counting -1), all drives will be formatted using a
        very lame hardware routine, which does not work on faster
        processors because of timing problem. The virus tries to
        cheat the user. It writes messages, that it is searching
        for virus etc. But it does not search, it simply uses the
        DOS delay routines to wait some seconds.

        Remember: This was a work of beginners. Some words to 
        you: Better play with your joysticks !!!
 
        This virus looks like a work of one hour. The formatroutine
        looks very similar to a routine published in a big german
        book company and the rest code is lame....
                
        "intuition.library"
        "df0:libs/Exec.library"
        "df0:Libs"
        "-*- Excreminator V1.0 -*-"
        "Written by ',27,'The Lame Trio (TLT)',27,' in 1991"
        "Memory Check ..."
        "Checking BootBlock for Virus ..."
        "  OK! No Virus found!"
        "ALL DRIVES FUCKED UP! LAME SUCKER !!!"
        "#Use a better Viruskiller next time!"
        "-e.g. Excreminator II HAHAHA"

                                        Detection tested:
                                        

                                                Somewhen in 1993
                                                
                                                

@endnode

