 VirusWorkshop Version 3.8 final:
 ---------------------------------

 > VirusWorkshop 3.8 is only for Kickstart 2.04 and higher.


 > It is not allowed to put VirusWorkshop on S.H.I. discs !
 > There are two exceptions:
 > Lars Kristensen and Jan Bo Andersen ( SHI Center in Denmark )


   Hiermit verbiete ich, Markus Schmall, Mallander Computersoftware
   VirusWorkshop zu vertreiben !!!!

   Don`t try to (de)crunch VirusWorkshop. It`s decrunchprotected and
   is already crunched !



   - Added Loop Combo Trojan(bomb).
   - Added a file, which is infected with the PP Bomb (MMaster 1.7).
   Thanks must go to Georg Hoermann for sending this virus.
   - "Bug" fix, I forgot to close the FileID library again. Fixed now.
   Thanks must go to Ingo Schmidt for reporting this bug.
   - Rewrote some intern routines to optimise the whole programm. The
   preferencesfile is now stored in the env: directory.
   - Rewrote Preferences Editor : Now it is possible to choose an
   resolution beetween 640*256 and 800*600 to work with VirusWorkshop.


   Caution ! New Preferences File format ! Simply use the new editor !
              Resolution must big higher then 640*256 !



   - Added support for the A4000(t) kickstart version 40.70 ! Thanks
   again to Ingo Schmidt for sending it !
   - Changed some other intern stuff, removed the display of the vbr and
   optimized (speeded up) some routines....

   - Added recognitioncode for the installer of Cascade 2.1 and Creeping
   Eel BB Viruses. Thanks again VirDown ! Welcome back on stage !
   - Added recognition code for Labtec Trojan Virus. Special thanks must
   go to Michael Arends of Amiga Virus Busters for sending this virus ! 
   - Thanks to Ingo Schmidt for some hints for the DriveInfo function
   (RAM DISK!!!). Thanks Ingo !
   - Added recognitioncode for the DMS 2.13 trojan. Special thanks go
   to Blind Guardian/TRSi for sending this virus ! THx !



   Markus



