   Thanx must go to Crackdown/Mystic for keeping this virus for me.
 - Added KAKO Bootvirus + Installer (Thanx must go to KARAM for sending
   this stuff)
 - Added new function in FILEREQ/SingleFile:If you select a file,
   only the file will be checked.If you select a directory,the whole
   directory will be checked.
